---
title: Venison Steak Sandwich with Cheese, Caramelised Onions and Chips
description: This Venison Steak Sandwich is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R11_W13_UK_HVP19085-3_Main_low-4c50ebfd.jpg
